| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2684 — Recovery Inhibition (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c9418ab4-470e-50d9-9eb5-38a63a8140ba"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
